sp.p:
              
              
                An other sweet youth too, I take it a Comfit-maker; 

                and it seems hath rotten teeth, for he dares not come in sight

                so long as the Barber is in the way.

              
              
                You may see by his hair he is a man of hot Liver; 

                he came over me with such violence I had not the heart

                to resist him.
